{
  "text": "To confirm that increases in SSC intensity did indeed indicate TiO 2 particle uptake, we undertook correlative studies with conventional flow cytometry and imaging cytometry which allows visualisation of TiO 2 uptake by individual cells [CITATION_1] . This technique was not available in the laboratory that undertook the above work and is impractical for a very large number of samples, so only the lower concentration range was investigated and correlated to ensure true discrimination from background.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "19277799"
